OL,3,CDriver dragged police officer along
OL,4,Croad after crash confrontation
OL,6,FA woman from has been banned from
OL,7,Fdriving after dragging a police
OL,8,Fofficer along the road as he
OL,9,Fconfronted her about an earlier
OL,10,Faccident.
OL,12,FLouise Hemmings, aged 39, had crashed
OL,13,Fher car into a parked vehicle and then
OL,14,Fdriven off in a panic.
OL,16,Fheard that an off-duty police
OL,17,Finspector was a neighbour of the man
OL,18,Fwhose car was hit and he went outside
OL,19,Fto investigate.
