OL,3,CDriver dragged police officer along
OL,4,Croad after crash confrontation
OL,6,FHe saw the car travelling up
OL,7,FMarlborough Avenue in Hornsea and
OL,8,Fdecided that he was going to try to
OL,9,Fstop the car.
OL,11,FHe stood in the middle of the road and
OL,12,Fshouted that he was an off-duty police
OL,13,Fofficer.
OL,15,FHull Crown Court was told that
OL,16,FHemmings stopped her car and he
OL,17,Fapproached and spoke to her and asked
OL,18,Fher to get out.
