OL,3,CDriver dragged police officer along
OL,4,Croad after crash confrontation
OL,6,F"She swore at him," said prosecutor Mr
OL,7,FBenjamin Donnell. "He attempted to
OL,8,Ftake the keys out of the defendant's
OL,9,Fignition. He heard her engine rev and
OL,10,Fshe drove off, dragging him along the
OL,11,Froad, causing bruising and scratches
OL,12,Fto his elbow and knees."
OL,14,FEarlier that evening Hemmings had
OL,15,Fcrashed her Vauxhall Meriva into the
OL,16,Fparked Citroen DS in Southgate,
OL,17,FHornsea at 11.15pm.
