OL,3,CDriver dragged police officer along
OL,4,Croad after crash confrontation
OL,6,FHer car was damaged at the front. The
OL,7,Fbonnet was damaged and the bumper was
OL,8,Fleft hanging off. The incident was
OL,9,Fcaught on CCTV.
OL,11,F"Her standard of driving that evening
OL,12,Ffell far below that which was expected
OL,13,Fof a competent and careful driver,"
OL,14,Fsaid Mr Donnell. "The condition of the
OL,15,Fdefendant's vehicle was dangerous to
OL,16,Fdrive and she decided to drive the
OL,17,Fvehicle onwards and not pull over. "
OL,19,FThe mother of the owner of the damaged
OL,20,Fcar tried to stop her but Hemmings
OL,21,Fdrove towards her.
