OL,3,CDriver dragged police officer along
OL,4,Croad after crash confrontation
OL,6,FThe woman told the court: "My aim was
OL,7,Fto get the registration number.
OL,8,FAdrenaline kicked in and, naively, I
OL,9,Fstood in the road. As the car came
OL,10,Ftowards me, I was sure it wasn't going
OL,11,Fto stop. I leapt on to the pavement. "
OL,13,FShe said she saw the off-duty officer
OL,14,F"fall to the floor and the car
OL,15,Fcontinued to drive towards me". She
OL,16,Fadded: "All I saw him doing was
OL,17,Fopening the car door. The car was
OL,18,Fstill moving and he was running
OL,19,Falongside the car."
