OL,3,CDriver dragged police officer along
OL,4,Croad after crash confrontation
OL,6,FHemmings told the court during her
OL,7,Fdefence that a cat ran out into the
OL,8,Froad before the crash and she did not
OL,9,Fhave time to brake and swerved.
OL,11,FShe claimed: "I panicked. I was so
OL,12,Fscared. I was frightened. I didn't
OL,13,Fknow whose car I had crashed into or
OL,14,Fwho was coming out to me."
OL,16,F"As far as I was concerned, that car
OL,17,Fwas okay to drive," she added. "I just
OL,18,Fneeded to stop and have a think about
OL,19,Fwhat I had just done and what am I
OL,20,Fgoing to do?"
