OL,3,CDriver dragged police officer along
OL,4,Croad after crash confrontation
OL,6,FHemmings claimed that she went back to
OL,7,Ftry to find a car that had been
OL,8,Fdamaged and that this was when she saw
OL,9,Fthe off-duty police officer.
OL,11,F"I originally thought that there was
OL,12,Fsomething wrong with him," she claimed.
OL,14,F"I stopped my car and wound my window
OL,15,Fdown. He came running towards my car.
OL,16,FHe was screaming and shouting. He put
OL,17,Fhis arm in my car while the window was
OL,18,Fdown and opened the door.
OL,20,F"He shouldn't have been doing what he
OL,21,Fwas doing."
