OL,3,CDriver dragged police officer along
OL,4,Croad after crash confrontation
OL,6,FShe added: "I was just trying to get
OL,7,Faway from the scene because I didn't
OL,8,Fwant to get into trouble."
OL,10,FShe had no previous convictions and
OL,11,Fhad a clean driving record.
OL,13,FHemmings, 39, of the Holderness Road
OL,14,Farea of east Hull, denied two offences
OL,15,Fof dangerous driving on October 29,
OL,16,F2022, but she was convicted by a jury
OL,17,Fafter a trial.
