OL,3,CDriver dragged police officer along
OL,4,Croad after crash confrontation
OL,6,FRecorder Richard Wright KC told
OL,7,FHemmings: "I reject completely your
OL,8,Fsuggestion that an animal had run out
OL,9,Finto the road, causing you to lose
OL,10,Fcontrol. My strong suspicion is that
OL,11,Fyou had been drinking alcohol that
OL,12,Fevening and that explained your
OL,13,Fdecision to drive off from the scene,
OL,14,Fbut I can't be sure of that."
OL,16,FHemmings was given 15 days'
OL,17,Frehabilitation.
